{"tid":2514324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"觀塘噴泉重開　增設規例告示牌　保安長期駐守","createTime":"2021-05-03T07:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T08:27:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":43,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"5d816d9b13a8b52f8bbaffacd7af0db8a95d0a1a","tid":2514324,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:41:31.000Z","msg":"耗資逾 5000 萬元興建的觀塘海濱音樂噴泉早前啟用 5 日後即停用，當局稱是因為池水疑受梘液影響出現大量泡沫而需徹底清潔。圍封停用一星期後，噴泉今日（3日）再次開放予公眾使用。<br />\n<br />\n記者在現場所見，噴水池旁邊增加了「遊樂場地規例」告示牌，其中包括條文「任何人不可於用作美化的湖、池塘、溪澗或水中沐浴、涉水或洗濯」。噴泉周邊亦增設近 20 個綠色橫額，提醒公眾禁止 4 人聚集。另有兩名保安長期駐足看守。<br />\n<br />\n下午二時許，天氣灰暗帶微雨，現場除了一眾記者外，只有不足 5 人駐足觀看噴水區，嬉水區則完全沒有小孩子到場玩樂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/181081524_4129257937159795_419531921311687247_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=973b4a&amp;_nc_ohc=l87DnpExflQAX9zCqY4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=4be5c9264d5690824bebe4c272f4e4e1&amp;oe=60B37224\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.6435-9%2F181081524_4129257937159795_419531921311687247_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D973b4a%26_nc_ohc%3Dl87DnpExflQAX9zCqY4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3D4be5c9264d5690824bebe4c272f4e4e1%26oe%3D60B37224&h=1736b0bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/4129257933826462/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F4129257933826462%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOP%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=a3310a36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/4129257933826462/</a>"},{"pid":"ca40ef2b6657a74d6221608686c54541dd9ddfcd","tid":2514324,"uid":246242,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:43:33.000Z","msg":"wow 個條例水蛇春咁長，揾鬼睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass